last_episode_to_air.overview: Prakan experiences time without Tuaphee; Tuaphee must make a decision that may cause him pain in the future.

name: Dear Doctor, I'm Coming for Soul
original_name: คุณหมอครับ ผมมารับวิญญาณคนไข้
overview: Dr. Prakan is a well-known surgeon dedicated to saving people’s lives. However, while he is trying to save lives he is constantly visited by the last person he could ever want to see. Death will show up every day trying to take the souls of the people that the doctor is trying to save. They work for completely opposing sides. One must collect the souls of the dead, the other must save lives before they reach that state. Is it possible to fall in love with the one thing you try to avoid, and how can the love story between death and a Doctor last?

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Prakan Pitakjiti is one of the most amazing surgeons in the hospital. He has a special gift which is the ability to see the angel of death. He called him Tua-Phee because he always shows up in the surgery room with a white ticket and it means that his patient won't survive any longer. Tua-Phee becomes the person who Prakan want to meet the least because his presence means his failure to save people. However, faith brings them together as it turns out that Tua-Phee is living next-door.

episodes.name: 1st Ticket
episodes.overview: While Prakan is hard at work saving lives at the hospital, he is frequented by an unwelcome visitor, Tua-Phee, a reaper of souls.

episodes.name: Memories Ticket
episodes.overview: After an organ transplant recipient learns of their donor's misdeeds, she is hesitant to accept the life-saving operation. Where the doctors fail to persuade her, only Tua-phee is able to change her mind.

episodes.name: Winning Ticket
episodes.overview: A competition begins between Prakan and Metha to decide who will become the next Head of Surgery a the hospital.

episodes.name: Ticket to the Sea
episodes.overview: After losing a bet, Prakan spend the day with Tuaphee at the beach.

episodes.name: Unwanted Ticket
episodes.overview: Prakan's work becomes personal when his friend Baas sustains life threatening injuries.

episodes.name: Lost Ticket
episodes.overview: Kheeta plans to confess his feelings to Prakan.  Prakan slowly realizes that Tuaphee is not the heartless soul-reaper that he first assumed.

episodes.name: Unexpected Ticket
episodes.overview: Tuaphee faces an impossible choice as Prakan's mother is about to pass away from cancer.

episodes.name: Death Ticket
episodes.overview: Nathee's father, who he has an estranged relationship with, ends up in the hospital.

episodes.name: Forgotten Ticket
episodes.overview: Khett opens up to Prakan about the rules of soul reapers, in an attempt to help him make amends with Tuaphee.

episodes.name: Ticket to the Truth Train
episodes.overview: Prakan suddenly recognized Tuaphee from before he died.  Nuch begins to attract the attention of a gentleman at the hospital, making Metha jealous.

episodes.name: Ticket to Underworld
episodes.overview: Prakan and Metha discover corruption within the hospital and confront the director.

episodes.name: Last Ticket
episodes.overview: Prakan experiences time without Tuaphee; Tuaphee must make a decision that may cause him pain in the future.
